          <text><![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><b>Accelerating Biomedical Research Act </b></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal">This bill amends the Balanced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985 to require certain adjustments to the annual discretionary spending limits for FY2019-FY2021 to accommodate increases in appropriations to the National Institutes of Health at the Department of Health and Human Services. </p>]]></text>
